<h1 id="四、自定义service"><a href="#四、自定义service" class="headerlink" title="四、自定义service"></a>四、自定义service</h1><h2 id="1-使用通用的service"><a href="#1-使用通用的service" class="headerlink" title="1. 使用通用的service"></a>1. 使用通用的service</h2><p>mybatis-plus提供了通用的ServiceI接口，其中定义了基本的CRUD操作方法，并且编写了对应的实现类ServiceImpl</p>
<ul>
<li><p>使用通用的service</p>
<ul>
<li><p>编写UserService接口继承ServiceI接口</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title">UserService</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">IService</span>&lt;<span class="title">User</span>&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编写UserServiceImpl实现类，继承ServiceImpl，实现UserService</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">UserServiceImpl</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">ServiceImpl</span>&lt;<span class="title">UserMapper</span>,<span class="title">User</span>&gt; <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">UserService</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="2-编写自定义service方法"><a href="#2-编写自定义service方法" class="headerlink" title="2. 编写自定义service方法"></a>2. 编写自定义service方法</h2><p>如果需要自定义service方法</p>
<ul>
<li>向UserService接口中添加对应的方法</li>
<li>在UserServiceImpl类中实现</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="五、mabatis-plus常用注解"><a href="#五、mabatis-plus常用注解" class="headerlink" title="五、mabatis-plus常用注解"></a>五、mabatis-plus常用注解</h1><h2 id="1-TableName"><a href="#1-TableName" class="headerlink" title="1. @TableName"></a>1. @TableName</h2><p><strong>设置实体类对应的表名</strong></p>
<p>解决表名和实体类的名字不一致的问题</p>
<ul>
<li>如果修改表名为t_user</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@TableName(&quot;t_user&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">User</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Long id;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String name;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Integer age;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String email;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="方法二"><a href="#方法二" class="headerlink" title="方法二"></a>方法二</h3><p>通过mybatis-plus全局配置，定义所有实体类的映射前缀</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">mybatis-plus:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">configuration:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">log-impl:</span> <span class="string">org.apache.ibatis.logging.stdout.StdOutImpl</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#设置Mybatis-Plus全局配置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">global-config:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">db-config:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">table-prefix:</span> <span class="string">t_</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="2-TableId"><a href="#2-TableId" class="headerlink" title="2. @TableId"></a>2. @TableId</h2><p><strong>设置实体类属性为对应的表的主键</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>作用在属性上</li>
</ul>
<p>mybatis-plus 默认将id作为主键</p>
<h3 id="2-1-如果表中主键不是id则需要额外指定"><a href="#2-1-如果表中主键不是id则需要额外指定" class="headerlink" title="2.1 如果表中主键不是id则需要额外指定"></a>2.1 如果表中主键不是id则需要额外指定</h3><ul>
<li>在实体类主键属性上添加@TableId注解</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@AllArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@NoArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">User</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@TableId</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Long uid;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String name;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Integer age;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String email;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="2-2-实体类主键属性名称与对应表主键名不同"><a href="#2-2-实体类主键属性名称与对应表主键名不同" class="headerlink" title="2.2 实体类主键属性名称与对应表主键名不同"></a>2.2 实体类主键属性名称与对应表主键名不同</h3><ul>
<li>设置@TableId中value属性为对应表主键名</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@AllArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@NoArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">User</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@TableId(value = &quot;uid&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Long id;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String name;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Integer age;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String email;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="2-3-自定义id生成方式"><a href="#2-3-自定义id生成方式" class="headerlink" title="2.3 自定义id生成方式"></a>2.3 自定义id生成方式</h3><p>mybatis-plus中默认使用雪花算法生成自定义id</p>
<p>我们可以通过@TableId中的type属性设置id生成方式</p>
<ul>
<li>AUTO为自增</li>
<li>ASSIGN_ID 雪花算法</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@AllArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@NoArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">User</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@TableId(value = &quot;uid&quot;,type = IdType.AUTO)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Long id;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String name;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Integer age;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String email;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>注意：</strong> 如果主动设置了id则不会使用mybatis-plus生成方式</p>
